style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">* Bootstrap 支持 Internet Explorer 8 及更高版本的 IE 浏览器。</p><p><br/></p>'),(21,'<h1 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"color_h1\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76);\">网格系统</span></h1><div class=\"tutintro\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: auto; min-height: 92px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">本章节我们将讲解 Bootstrap 的网格系统（Grid System）。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Bootstrap 提供了一套响应式、移动设备优先的流式网格系统，随着屏幕或视口（viewport）尺寸的增加，系统会自动分为最多12列。</p></div><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">什么是网格（Grid）？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">摘自维基百科：</p><blockquote style=\"border: 0px; margin: 10px; padding: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(243, 247, 240);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/images/quote.png\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/>在平面设计中，网格是一种由一系列用于组织内容的相交的直线（垂直的、水平的）组成的结构（通常是二维的）。它广泛应用于打印设计中的设计布局和内容结构。在网页设计中，它是一种用于快速创建一致的布局和有效地使用 HTML 和 CSS 的方法。</blockquote><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">简单地说，网页设计中的网格用于组织内容，让网站易于浏览，并降低用户端的负载。</p><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">什么是 Bootstrap 网格系统（Grid System）？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 官方文档中有关网格系统的描述：</p><blockquote style=\"border: 0px; margin: 10px; padding: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(243, 247, 240);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/images/quote.png\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/>Bootstrap 包含了一个响应式的、移动设备优先的、不固定的网格系统，可以随着设备或视口大小的增加而适当地扩展到 12 列。它包含了用于简单的布局选项的预定义类，也包含了用于生成更多语义布局的功能强大的混合类。</blockquote><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">让我们来理解一下上面的语句。Bootstrap 3 是移动设备优先的，在这个意义上，Bootstrap 代码从小屏幕设备（比如移动设备、平板电脑）开始，然后扩展到大屏幕设备（比如笔记本电脑、台式电脑）上的组件和网格。</p><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">移动设备优先策略</h3><ul style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><strong>内容</strong><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none;\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">决定什么是最重要的。</li></ul></li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><strong>布局</strong><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none;\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">优先设计更小的宽度。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">基础的 CSS 是移动设备优先，媒体查询是针对于平板电脑、台式电脑。</li></ul></li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><strong>渐进增强</strong><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none;\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">随着屏幕大小的增加而添加元素。</li></ul></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">响应式网格系统随着屏幕或视口（viewport）尺寸的增加，系统会自动分为最多12列。</p><table class=\"grid\" style=\"border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 730px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 240);\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">1</td></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><td colspan=\"4\" style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">4</td><td colspan=\"4\" style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">4</td><td colspan=\"4\" style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">4</td></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><td colspan=\"4\" style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">4</td><td colspan=\"8\" style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">8</td></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><td colspan=\"6\" style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">6</td><td colspan=\"6\" style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">6</td></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><td colspan=\"12\" style=\"border: 4px solid white; margin: 0px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em;\">12</td></tr></tbody></table><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 网格系统（Grid System）的工作原理</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网格系统通过一系列包含内容的行和列来创建页面布局。下面列出了 Bootstrap 网格系统是如何工作的：</p><ul style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">行必须放置在<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.container</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>class 内，以便获得适当的对齐（alignment）和内边距（padding）。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用行来创建列的水平组。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">内容应该放置在列内，且唯有列可以是行的直接子元素。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">预定义的网格类，比如<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.row</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>和<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.col-xs-4</strong>，可用于快速创建网格布局。LESS 混合类可用于更多语义布局。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">列通过内边距（padding）来创建列内容之间的间隙。该内边距是通过<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.rows</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>上的外边距（margin）取负，表示第一列和最后一列的行偏移。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">网格系统是通过指定您想要横跨的十二个可用的列来创建的。例如，要创建三个相等的列，则使用三个<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.col-xs-4</strong>。</li></ul><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">媒体查询</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">媒体查询是非常别致的&quot;有条件的 CSS 规则&quot;。它只适用于一些基于某些规定条件的 CSS。如果满足那些条件，则应用相应的样式。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 中的媒体查询允许您基于视口大小移动、显示并隐藏内容。下面的媒体查询在 LESS 文件中使用，用来创建 Bootstrap 网格系统中的关键的分界点阈值。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">/* 超小设备（手机，小于 768px） */\r\n/* Bootstrap 中默认情况下没有媒体查询 */\r\n\r\n/* 小型设备（平板电脑，768px 起） */\r\n@media (min-width: @screen-sm-min) { ... }\r\n\r\n/* 中型设备（台式电脑，992px 起） */\r\n@media (min-width: @screen-md-min) { ... }\r\n\r\n/* 大型设备（大台式电脑，1200px 起） */\r\n@media (min-width: @screen-lg-min) { ... }</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们有时候也会在媒体查询代码中包含<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>max-width</strong>，从而将 CSS 的影响限制在更小范围的屏幕大小之内。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">@media (max-width: @screen-xs-max) { ... }\r\n@media (min-width: @screen-sm-min) and (max-width: @screen-sm-max) { ... }\r\n@media (min-width: @screen-md-min) and (max-width: @screen-md-max) { ... }\r\n@media (min-width: @screen-lg-min) { ... }</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">媒体查询有两个部分，先是一个设备规范，然后是一个大小规则。在上面的案例中，设置了下列的规则：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">让我们来看下面这行代码：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">@media (min-width: @screen-sm-min) and (max-width: @screen-sm-max) { ... }</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于所有带有<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>min-width: @screen-sm-min</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>的设备，如果屏幕的宽度小于<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>@screen-sm-max</em>，则会进行一些处理。</p><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsof