-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><p><br/></p><p></p>'),(50,'<p></p><p></p><h1 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"color_h1\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76);\">面板（Panels）</span></h1><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本章将讲解 Bootstrap 面板（Panels）。面板组件用于把 DOM 组件插入到一个盒子中。创建一个基本的面板，只需要向 &lt;div&gt; 元素添加 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.panel</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>和 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.panel-default</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>即可，如下面的实例所示：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 默认的面板&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link href=&quot;/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot; rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/scripts/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;panel panel-default&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;panel-body&quot;&gt;\r\n      这是一个基本的面板\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p><br/></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/paneldeafult_demo.jpg\" alt=\"默认的面板\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">面板标题</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们可以通过以下两种方式来添加面板标题：</p><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.panel-heading</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>class 可以很简单地向面板添加标题容器。to easily add a heading container to your panel.</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用带有<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.panel-title</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>class 的 &lt;h1&gt;-&lt;h6&gt; 来添加预定义样式的标题。</li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面的实例演示了这两种方式：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 面板标题&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link href=&quot;/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot; rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/scripts/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;panel panel-default&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;panel-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n      不带 title 的面板标题\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;panel-body&quot;&gt;\r\n      面板内容\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;panel panel-default&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;panel-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;h3 class=&quot;panel-title&quot;&gt;\r\n         带有 title 的面板标题\r\n      &lt;/h3&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;panel-body&quot;&gt;\r\n      面板内容\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p><br/></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/panelheading_demo.jpg\" alt=\"面板标题\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">面板脚注</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们可以在面板中添加脚注，只需要把按钮或者副文本放在带有 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.panel-footer</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>的 &lt;div&gt; 中即可。下面的实例演示了这点：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0