 margin: 0px; padding: 3px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: top; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">选项名称</th><th style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(85, 85, 85); margin: 0px; padding: 3px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: top; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">类型/默认值</th><th style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(85, 85, 85); margin: 0px; padding: 3px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: top; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Data 属性名称</th><th style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(85, 85, 85); margin: 0px; padding: 3px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: top; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">描述</th></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">animation</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">boolean<br/><em>默认值：true</em></td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">data-animation</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">向弹出框应用 CSS 褪色过渡效果。</td></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 240);\"><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">html</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">boolean<br/><em>默认值：false</em></td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">data-html</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212