insert  into `t_content_ext`(`content_id`,`txt`) values (83,'<p></p><h1 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"color_h1\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76);\">折叠（Collapse）插件</span></h1><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">折叠（Collapse）插件可以很容易地让页面区域折叠起来。无论您用它来创建折叠导航还是内容面板，它都允许很多内容选项。</p><blockquote style=\"border: 0px; margin: 10px; padding: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(243, 247, 240);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/images/quote.png\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/>如果您想要单独引用该插件的功能，那么您需要引用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>collapse.js</strong>。同时，也需要在您的 Bootstrap 版本中引用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a target=\"_self\" href=\"http://www.coding17.com/bootstrap/plugins/2016030753.html\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: none; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">Transition（过渡）插件</a>。或者，正如<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.coding17.com/bootstrap/plugins/2016030752.html\" target=\"_self\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: none; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">Bootstrap 插件概览</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>一章中所提到，您可以引用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>bootstrap.js</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>或压缩版的<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>bootstrap.min.js</em>。</blockquote><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">您可以使用折叠（Collapse）插件：</p><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><em><strong>创建可折叠的分组或折叠面板（accordion）</strong></em>，如下所示：<pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 折叠面板&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link href=&quot;/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot; rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/scripts/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;panel-group&quot; id=&quot;accordion&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=&quot;panel panel-default&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;div class=&quot;panel-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;h4 class=&quot;panel-title&quot;&gt;\r\n        &lt;a data-toggle=&quot;collapse&quot; data-parent=&quot;#accordion&quot; \r\n          href=&quot;#collapseOne&quot;&gt;\r\n          点击我进行展开，再次点击我进行折叠。第 1 部分\r\n        &lt;/a&gt;\r\n      &lt;/h4&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=&quot;collapseOne&quot; class=&quot;panel-collapse collapse in&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;panel-body&quot;&gt;\r\n        Nihil anim keffiyeh helvetica, craft 