rder: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px;\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/accordion_demo.jpg\" alt=\"折叠面板\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><ol class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; list-style-type: none;\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 2.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; list-style-type: decimal; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><strong>data-toggle=&quot;collapse&quot;</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>添加到您想要展开或折叠的组件的链接上。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 2.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; list-style-type: decimal; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><strong>href</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>或<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>data-target</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性添加到父组件，它的值是子组件的<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>id</em>。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 2.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; list-style-type: decimal; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><strong>data-parent</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性把折叠面板（accordion）的 id 添加到要展开或折叠的组件的链接上。</li></ol></li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; b