ob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">属性<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>data-slide</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>接受关键字<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>prev</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>或<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>next</em>，用来改变幻灯片相对于当前位置的位置。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>data-slide-to</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>来向轮播床底一个原始滑动索引，<strong>data-slide-to=&quot;2&quot;</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>将把滑块移动到一个特定的索引，索引从 0 开始计数。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><strong>data-ride=&quot;carousel&quot;</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性用于标记轮播在页面加载时就开始动画播放。</li></ul></li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><strong>通过 JavaScript</strong>：轮播（Carousel）可通过 JavaScript 手动调用，如下所示：<pre class=\"prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: no