-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">15.&nbsp;<a href=\"http://paintstrap.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: none; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">PaintStrap</a></h3><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PaintStrap 使用 Adobe kuler/COLOURlovers 颜色组合来生成漂亮的 Twitter Bootstrap 主题。这个工具特别容易安装，同时很容易下载 CSS 文件并且也很容易替换成另一个标准的文件。</span><img class=\"attachment-full\" alt=\"22215744_BxJa\" src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/22215744_BxJa.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" height=\"310\" width=\"550\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span> <br/></span><p><br/></p>'),(90,'<h1 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 10px;padding: 0px;font-size: 2.1em;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 0px;font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bootstrap HTML编码规范</h1><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">语法</h2><ul style=\"border: 0px;margin: 1em 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 16.7999992370605px;list-style-type: none;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\">用两个空格来代替制表符（tab） -- 这是唯一能保证在所有环境下获得一致展现的方法。</li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\">嵌套元素应当缩进一次（即两个空格）。</li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\">对于属性的定义，确保全部使用双引号，绝不要使用单引号。</li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\">不要在自闭合（self-closing）元素的尾部添加斜线 --<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://dev.w3.org/html5/spec-author-view/syntax.html#syntax-start-tag\" style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(100, 133, 76);-webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s;transition: opacity 0.2s\">HTML5 规范</a>中明确说明这是可选的。</li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\">不要省略可选的结束标签（closing tag）（例如，<code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">&lt;/li&gt;</code><span>&nbsp;</span>或<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">&lt;/body&gt;</code>）。</li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">实例：</p><pre style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin: 15px auto;padding: 10px 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt; &lt;html&gt;   &lt;head&gt;     &lt;title&gt;Page title&lt;/title&gt;   &lt;/head&gt;   &lt;body&gt;     &lt;img src=&quot;images/company-logo.png&quot; alt=&quot;Company&quot;&gt;     &lt;h1&gt;Hello, world!&lt;/h1&gt;   &lt;/body&gt; &lt;/html&gt; </pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">HTML5 doctype</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">为每个 HTML 页面的第一行添加标准模式（standard mode）的声明，这样能够确保在每个浏览器中拥有一致的展现。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">实例：</p><pre style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin: 15px auto;padding: 10px 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt; &lt;html&gt;   &lt;head&gt;   &lt;/head&gt; &lt;/html&gt; </pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">语言属性</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">根据 HTML5 规范：</p><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">强烈建议为 html 根元素指定 lang 属性，从而为文档设置正确的语言。这将有助于语音合成工具确定其所应该采用的发音，有助于翻译工具确定其翻译时所应遵守的规则等等。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">更多关于<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">lang</code><span>&nbsp;</span>属性的知识可以从<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.w3.org/html/wg/drafts/html/master/semantics.html#the-html-element\" style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(100, 133, 76);-webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s;transition: opacity 0.2s\">此规范</a><span>&nbsp;</span>中了解。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">这里列出了<a href=\"http://reference.sitepoint.com/html/lang-codes\" style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(100, 133, 76);-webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s;transition: opacity 0.2s\">语言代码表</a>。</p><pre style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin: 15px auto;padding: 10px 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&lt;html&gt;   &lt;!-- ... --&gt; &lt;/html&gt; </pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">IE 兼容模式</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">IE 支持通过特定的<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">&lt;meta&gt;</code><span>&nbsp;</span>标签来确定绘制当前页面所应该采用的 IE 版本。除非有强烈的特殊需求，否则最好是设置为<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px\">edge mode</strong>，从而通知 IE 采用其所支持的最新的模式。</p><pre style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin: 15px auto;padding: 10px 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;X-UA-Compatible&quot; content=&quot;IE=Edge&quot;&gt; </pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">字符编码</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">通过明确声明字符编码，能够确保浏览器快速并容易的判断页面内容的渲染方式。这样做的好处是，可以避免在 HTML 中使用字符实体标记（character entity），从而全部与文档编码一致（一般采用 UTF-8 编码）。</p><pre style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin: 15px auto;padding: 10px 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&lt;head&gt;   &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt; &lt;/head&gt; </pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">引入 CSS 和 JavaScript 文件</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">根据 HTML5 规范，在引入 CSS 和 JavaScript 文件时一般不需要指定<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">type</code><span>&nbsp;</span>属性，因为<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">text/css</code><span>&nbsp;</span>和<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">text/javascript</code><span>&nbsp;</span>分别是它们的默认值。</p><h3 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 8px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.4em;font-weight: 700;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">HTML5 spec links</h3><ul style=\"border: 0px;margin: 1em 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 16.7999992370605px;list-style-type: none;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\"><a href=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/2011/WD-html5-20110525/semantics.html#the-link-element\" style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(100, 133, 76);-webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s;transition: opacity 0.2s\">Using link</a></li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\"><a href=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/2011/WD-html5-20110525/semantics.html#the-style-element\" style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(100, 133, 76);-webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s;transition: opacity 0.2s\">Using style</a></li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\"><a href=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/2011/WD-html5-20110525/scripting-1.html#the-script-element\" style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(100, 133, 76);-webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s;transition: opacity 0.2s\">Using script</a></li></ul><pre style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin: 15px auto;padding: 10px 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&lt;!-- External CSS --&gt; &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;code-guide.css&quot;&gt; &lt;!-- In-document CSS --&gt; &lt;style&gt;   /* ... */ &lt;/style&gt; &lt;!-- JavaScript --&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;code-guide.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; </pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">实用为王</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">尽量遵循 HTML 标准和语义，但是不要以牺牲实用性为代价。任何时候都要尽量使用最少的标签并保持最小的复杂度。</p><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">属性顺序</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">HTML 属性应当按照以下给出的顺序依次排列，确保代码的易读性。</p><ul style=\"border: 0px;margin: 1em 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 16.7999992370605px;list-style-type: none;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\"><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">class</code></li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\"><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">id</code>,<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">name</code></li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\"><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">data-*</code></li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\"><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">src</code>,<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">for</code>,<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">type</code>,<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">href</code></li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\"><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">title</code>,<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">alt</code></li><li style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;background-position: 0% 0.5em;background-repeat: no-repeat\"><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">aria-*</code>,<span>&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px;padding: 2px 4px;font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(212, 73, 80);border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem;border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem;border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249)\">role</code></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">class 用于标识高度可复用组件，因此应该排在首位。id 用于标识具体组件，应当谨慎使用（例如，页面内的书签），因此排在第二位。</p><pre style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin: 15px auto;padding: 10px 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&lt;a class=&quot;...&quot; id=&quot;...&quot; data-modal=&quot;toggle&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;   Example link &lt;/a&gt; &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot;&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;...&quot; alt=&quot;...&quot;&gt; </pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">布尔（boolean）型属性</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">布尔型属性可以在声明时不赋值。XHTML 规范要求为其赋值，但是 HTML5 规范不需要。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">更多信息请参考<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/common-microsyntaxes.html#boolean-attributes\" style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(100, 133, 76);-webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s;transition: opacity 0.2s\">WhatWG section on boolean attributes</a>：</p><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">元素的布尔型属性如果有值，就是 true，如果没有值，就是 false。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">如果<em style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px\">一定</em>要为其赋值的话，请参考 WhatWG 规范：</p><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">如果属性存在，其值必须是空字符串或 [...] 属性的规范名称，并且不要再收尾添加空白符。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px\">简单来说，就是不用赋值。</strong></p><pre style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin: 15px auto;padding: 10px 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; disabled&gt; &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;1&quot; checked&gt; &lt;select&gt;   &lt;option value=&quot;1&quot; selected&gt;1&lt;/option&gt; &lt;/select&gt; </pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">减少标签的数量</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">编写 HTML 代码时，尽量避免多余的父元素。很多时候，这需要迭代和重构来实现。请看下面的案例：</p><pre style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin: 15px auto;padding: 10px 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&lt;!-- Not so great --&gt; &lt;span&gt;   &lt;img src=&quot;...&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;!-- Better --&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;...&quot;&gt; </pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px;margin: 2px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">JavaScript 生成的标签</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 2em;font-size: 12px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">通过 JavaScript 生成的标签让内容变得不易查找、编辑，并且降低性能。能避免时尽量避免。</p><p><br/></p>'),(91,'<h1 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap CSS编码规范</h1><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">语法</h2><ul style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">用两个空格来代替制表符（tab） -- 这是唯一能保证在所有环境下获得一致展现的方法。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">为选择器分组时，将单独的选择器单独放在一行。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">为了代码的易读性，在每个声明块的左花括号前添加一个空格。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">声明块的右花括号应当单独成行。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">每条声明语句的<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">:</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>后应该插入一个空格。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">为了获得更准确的错误报告，每条声明都应该独占一行。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">所有声明语句都应当以分号结尾。最后一条声明语句后面的分号是可选的，但是，如果省略这个分号，你的代码可能更易出错。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">对于以逗号分隔的属性值，每个逗号后面都应该插入一个空格（例如，<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">box-shadow</code>）。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">不要在<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">rgb()</code>、<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">rgba()</code>、<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">hsl()</code>、<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">hsla()</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>或<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">rect()</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>值的<em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">内部</em>的逗号后面插入空格。这样利于从多个属性值（既加逗号也加空格）中区分多个颜色值（只加逗号，不加空格）。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">对于属性值或颜色参数，省略小于 1 的小数前面的 0 （例如，<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">.5</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>代替<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">0.5</code>；<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">-.5px</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>代替<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">-0.5px</code>）。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">十六进制值应该全部小写，例如，<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">#fff</code>。在扫描文档时，小写字符易于分辨，因为他们的形式更易于区分。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">尽量使用简写形式的十六进制值，例如，用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">#fff</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>代替<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">#ffffff</code>。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">为选择器中的属性添加双引号，例如，<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">input[type=&quot;text&quot;]</code>。<a href=\"http://mathiasbynens.be/notes/unquoted-attribute-values#css\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: none; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">只有在某些情况下是可选的</a>，但是，为了代码的一致性，建议都加上双引号。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">避免为 0 值指定单位，例如，用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">margin: 0;</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>代替<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">margin: 0px;</code>。</li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于这里用到的术语有疑问吗？请参考 Wikipedia 上的<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%A0%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F%E8%A1%A8#.E8.AF.AD.E6.B3.95\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">层叠样式表 - 语法</a>。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">/* Bad CSS */\r\n.selector, .selector-secondary, .selector[type=text] {\r\n  padding:15px;\r\n  margin:0px 0px 15px;\r\n  background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\r\n  box-shadow:0px 1px 2px #CCC,inset 0 1px 0 #FFFFFF\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* Good CSS */\r\n.selector,\r\n.selector-secondary,\r\n.selector[type=&quot;text&quot;] {\r\n  padding: 15px;\r\n  margin-bottom: 15px;\r\n  background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.5);\r\n  box-shadow: 0 1px 2px #ccc, inset 0 1px 0 #fff;\r\n}</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">声明顺序</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">相关的属性声明应当归为一组，并按照下面的顺序排列：</p><ol style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 2.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; list-style-type: decimal;\">Positioning</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 2.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; list-style-type: decimal;\">Box model</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 2.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; list-style-type: decimal;\">Typographic</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 2.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; list-style-type: decimal;\">Visual</li></ol><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由于定位（positioning）可以从正常的文档流中移除元素，并且还能覆盖盒模型（box model）相关的样式，因此排在首位。盒模型排在第二位，因为它决定了组件的尺寸和位置。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">其他属性只是影响组件的<em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">内部（inside）</em>或者是不影响前两组属性，因此排在后面。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">完整的属性列表及其排列顺序请参考<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://twitter.github.com/recess\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">Recess</a>。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">.declaration-order {\r\n  /* Positioning */\r\n  position: absolute;\r\n  top: 0;\r\n  right: 0;\r\n  bottom: 0;\r\n  left: 0;\r\n  z-index: 100;\r\n\r\n  /* Box-model */\r\n  display: block;\r\n  float: right;\r\n  width: 100px;\r\n  height: 100px;\r\n\r\n  /* Typography */\r\n  font: normal 13px &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;\r\n  line-height: 1.5;\r\n  color: #333;\r\n  text-align: center;\r\n\r\n  /* Visual */\r\n  background-color: #f5f5f5;\r\n  border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;\r\n  border-radius: 3px;\r\n\r\n  /* Misc */\r\n  opacity: 1;\r\n}</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不要使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">@import</code></h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">与<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">&lt;link&gt;</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>标签相比，<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">@import</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>指令要慢很多，不光增加了额外的请求次数，还会导致不可预料的问题。替代办法有以下几种：</p><ul style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用多个<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">&lt;link&gt;</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>元素</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">通过 Sass 或 Less 类似的 CSS 预处理器将多个 CSS 文件编译为一个文件</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">通过 Rails、Jekyll 或其他系统中提供过 CSS 文件合并功能</li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">请参考<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.stevesouders.com/blog/2009/04/09/dont-use-import/\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">Steve Souders 的文章</a>了解更多知识。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!-- Use link elements --&gt;\r\n&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;core.css&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;!-- Avoid @imports --&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\n  @import url(&quot;more.css&quot;);\r\n&lt;/style&gt;</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">媒体查询（Media query）的位置</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">将媒体查询放在尽可能相关规则的附近。不要将他们打包放在一个单一样式文件中或者放在文档底部。如果你把他们分开了，将来只会被大家遗忘。下面给出一个典型的实例。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">.element { ... }\r\n.element-avatar { ... }\r\n.element-selected { ... }\r\n\r\n@media (min-width: 480px) {\r\n  .element { ...}\r\n  .element-avatar { ... }\r\n  .element-selected { ... }\r\n}</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">带前缀的属性</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当使用特定厂商的带有前缀的属性时，通过缩进的方式，让每个属性的值在垂直方向对齐，这样便于多行编辑。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在 Textmate 中，使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Text → Edit Each Line in Selection</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>(⌃⌘A)。在 Sublime Text 2 中，使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Selection → Add Previous Line</strong>(⌃⇧↑) 和<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Selection → Add Next Line</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>(⌃⇧↓)。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">/* Prefixed properties */\r\n.selector {\r\n  -webkit-box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.15);\r\n          box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.15);\r\n}</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">单行规则声明</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">只包含一条声明</strong>的样式，为了易读性和便于快速编辑，建议将语句放在同一行。对于带有多条声明的样式，还是应当将声明分为多行。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这样做的关键因素是为了错误检测 -- 例如，CSS 校验器指出在 183 行有语法错误。如果是单行单条声明，你就不会忽略这个错误；如果是单行多条声明的话，你就要仔细分析避免漏掉错误了。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">/* Single declarations on one line */\r\n.span1 { width: 60px; }\r\n.span2 { width: 140px; }\r\n.span3 { width: 220px; }\r\n\r\n/* Multiple declarations, one per line */\r\n.sprite {\r\n  display: inline-block;\r\n  width: 16px;\r\n  height: 15px;\r\n  background-image: url(../img/sprite.png);\r\n}\r\n.icon           { background-position: 0 0; }\r\n.icon-home      { background-position: 0 -20px; }\r\n.icon-account   { background-position: 0 -40px; }</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">简写形式的属性声明</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在需要显示地设置所有值的情况下，应当尽量限制使用简写形式的属性声明。常见的滥用简写属性声明的情况如下：</p><ul style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">padding</code></li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">margin</code></li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">font</code></li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">background</code></li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">border</code></li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">border-radius</code></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">大部分情况下，我们不需要为简写形式的属性声明指定所有值。例如，HTML 的 heading 元素只需要设置上、下边距（margin）的值，因此，在必要的时候，只需覆盖这两个值就可以。过度使用简写形式的属性声明会导致代码混乱，并且会对属性值带来不必要的覆盖从而引起意外的副作用。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">MDN（Mozilla Developer Network）上一片非常好的关于<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">shorthand properties</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>的文章，对于不太熟悉简写属性声明及其行为的用户很有用。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">/* Bad example */\r\n.element {\r\n  margin: 0 0 10px;\r\n  background: red;\r\n  background: url(&quot;image.jpg&quot;);\r\n  border-radius: 3px 3px 0 0;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* Good example */\r\n.element {\r\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\r\n  background-color: red;\r\n  background-image: url(&quot;image.jpg&quot;);\r\n  border-top-left-radius: 3px;\r\n  border-top-right-radius: 3px;\r\n}</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Less 和 Sass 中的嵌套</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">避免非必要的嵌套。这是因为虽然你可以使用嵌套，但是并不意味着应该使用嵌套。只有在必须将样式限制在父元素内（也就是后代选择器），并且存在多个需要嵌套的元素时才使用嵌套。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">// Without nesting\r\n.table &gt; thead &gt; tr &gt; th { … }\r\n.table &gt; thead &gt; tr &gt; td { … }\r\n\r\n// With nesting\r\n.table &gt; thead &gt; tr {\r\n  &gt; th { … }\r\n  &gt; td { … }\r\n}</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注释</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">代码是由人编写并维护的。请确保你的代码能够自描述、注释良好并且易于他人理解。好的代码注释能够传达上下文关系和代码目的。不要简单地重申组件或 class 名称。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于较长的注释，务必书写完整的句子；对于一般性注解，可以书写简洁的短语。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">/* Bad example */\r\n/* Modal header */\r\n.modal-header {\r\n  ...\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* Good example */\r\n/* Wrapping element for .modal-title and .modal-close */\r\n.modal-header {\r\n  ...\r\n}</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">class 命名</h2><ul style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">class 名称中只能出现小写字符和破折号（dashe）（不是下划线，也不是驼峰命名法）。破折号应当用于相关 class 的命名（类似于命名空间）（例如，<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">.btn</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>和<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">.btn-danger</code>）。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">避免过度任意的简写。<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">.btn</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>代表<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">button</em>，但是<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">.s</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>不能表达任何意思。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">class 名称应当尽可能短，并且意义明确。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用有意义的名称。使用有组织的或目的明确的名称，不要使用表现形式（presentational）的名称。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">基于最近的父 class 或基本（base） class 作为新 class 的前缀。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">.js-*</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>class 来标识行为（与样式相对），并且不要将这些 class 包含到 CSS 文件中。</li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在为 Sass 和 Less 变量命名是也可以参考上面列出的各项规范。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">/* Bad example */\r\n.t { ... }\r\n.red { ... }\r\n.header { ... }\r\n\r\n/* Good example */\r\n.tweet { ... }\r\n.important { ... }\r\n.tweet-header { ... }</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">选择器</h2><ul style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">对于通用元素使用 class ，这样利于渲染性能的优化。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">对于经常出现的组件，避免使用属性选择器（例如，<code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">[class^=&quot;...&quot;]</code>）。浏览器的性能会受到这些因素的影响。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">选择器要尽可能短，并且尽量限制组成选择器的元素个数，建议不要超过 3 。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">只有</strong>在必要的时候才将 class 限制在最近的父元素内（也就是后代选择器）（例如，不使用带前缀的 class 时 -- 前缀类似于命名空间）。</li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">扩展阅读：</p><ul style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><a href=\"http://markdotto.com/2012/02/16/scope-css-classes-with-prefixes/\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: none; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">Scope CSS classes with prefixes</a></li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><a href=\"http://markdotto.com/2012/03/02/stop-the-cascade/\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: none; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">Stop the cascade</a></li></ul><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">/* Bad example */\r\nspan { ... }\r\n.page-container #stream .stream-item .tweet .tweet-header .username { ... }\r\n.avatar { ... }\r\n\r\n/* Good example */\r\n.avatar { ... }\r\n.tweet-header .username { ... }\r\n.tweet .avatar { ... }</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">代码组织</h2><ul style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">以组件为单位组织代码段。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">制定一致的注释规范。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用一致的空白符将代码分隔成块，这样利于扫描较大的文档。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">如果使用了多个 CSS 文件，将其按照组件而非页面的形式分拆，因为页面会被重组，而组件只会被移动。</li></ul><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">/*\r\n * Component section heading\r\n */\r\n\r\n.element { ... }\r\n\r\n\r\n/*\r\n * Component section heading\r\n *\r\n * Sometimes you need to include optional context for the entire component. Do that up here if it&#39;s important enough.\r\n */\r\n\r\n.element { ... }\r\n\r\n/* Contextual sub-component or modifer */\r\n.element-heading { ... }</pre><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">编辑器配置</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">将你的编辑器按照下面的配置进行设置，以避免常见的代码不一致和差异：</p><ul style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">用两个空格代替制表符（soft-tab 即用空格代表 tab 符）。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">保存文件时，删除尾部的空白符。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">设置文件编码为 UTF-8。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">在文件结尾添加一个空白行。</li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">参照文档并将这些配置信息添加到项目的<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &#39;PT Mono&#39;, Menlo, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(212, 73, 80); border-top-left-radius: 0.2rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.2rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.2rem; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249);\">.editorconfig</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>文件中。例如：<a href=\"https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/blob/master/.editorconfig\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">Bootstrap 中的 .editorconfig 实例</a>。更多信息请参考<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://editorconfig.org/\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">about EditorConfig</a>。</p><p><br/></p>'),(92,'<p></p><h1 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">HTML 教程-<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"color_h1\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76);\">(HTML5 标准)</span></h1><div class=\"tutintro\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: auto; min-height: 92px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">您可以使用 HTML 来建立自己的 WEB 站点。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">在本教程中，您将学习如何使用 HTML 来创建站点。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">HTML 很容易学习！相信您能很快学会它！</p></div><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">HTML 实例</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本教程包含了数百个 HTML 实例。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使用本站的编辑器，您可以轻松实现在线修改 HTML，并查看实例运行结果。</p><blockquote style=\"border: 0px; margin: 10px; pa